rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0001
rows.name:
Everyone, good morning.
Did you sleep well?

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0004
rows.name:
How about we take a nice stroll over
to the emergency summit hall?
Might help clear our heads a bit

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0005
rows.name:
Gotta make sure Meleph
gets there properly, right?

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0006
rows.name:
I think I would be perfectly capable
of finding my own way...

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0007
rows.name: Besides, Hikari was also invited, right?

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0009
rows.name: See? Perfect timing, don't ya think?

rows.label: fev06_040_150_msg0010
rows.name:
Yeah, you're right...
Let's get going.
